==English==

===Intransitive verb===
{{en-verb|surviv|ing}}

# Of a person, to continue to [[live]]; to remain [[alive]].
# Of an object or concept, to continue to [[exist]].

====Translations====
'''person: continue to live'''
{{top}}
*Finnish: [[selviytyä]], [[jäädä henkiin]], [[jäädä eloon]]
{{mid}}
