{{bottom}}

'''object, concept: continue to exist'''
{{top}}
{{mid}}
{{bottom}}

===Transitive verb===
{{en-verb|surviv|ing}}

# To [[live]] longer than.
#:''He was '''survived''' by his spouse and three children.''

====Synonyms====
*(''live longer than''): [[outlive]]

====Antonyms====
*(''live longer than''): [[predecease]]

